Wizz Air launched six flights from Odessa

04 Nov 2019, 13:47

The Hungarian low-cost airline Wizz Air performed its first flights from Odessa on November 1-4, 2019:

Odessa - Budapest;
Odessa - Berlin;
Odessa - Bratislava;
Odessa - Gdansk;
Odessa - Wroclaw;
Odessa - Katowice.

According to the press service of the airline, flights on these routes will be carried out twice a week.
Their cost is from 429 UAH one way with hand luggage.

